        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What You Get</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">24/7 Online Booking:</strong> Clients book anytime. You wake up to new reservations instead of voicemails.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Real-Time Capacity:</strong> The system knows which kennels are available. No more double-booking disasters.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-brand-navy">Vaccination Alerts:</strong> Never let an unvaccinated dog through again. Automatic reminders to owners before expiry.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-red flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
