        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What is kennel software?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Kennel software is a digital management platform designed specifically for pet boarding facilities. It handles bookings, room assignments, vaccination tracking, feeding schedules, payment processing, and customer communication.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
